title: $4 Dessert Vs. $235 Dessert
author: About To Eat
description:
Steven, Andrew, and Adam travel to three restaurants, trying the same food at three price points, to see which is the most worth it. In this episode they’re trying dessert experiences.

0:00 Intro
0:40 $ El Cochinito
5:13 Dessert fact
5:46 $$ Alta Adams
10:44 Dessert cheese detour
13:43 Dessert fact
14:14 $$$ Spago Beverly Hills
23:43 Worth It winners

About To Eat: A new YouTube channel from your internet food friends.
About To Eat is the excitement of knowing something wonderful is coming.
-Inga, Andrew, Adam, Annie, Liza, Alvin, Rie, Jody (and more)
